cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it focuses on unsupervised learning of state representations. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with reinforcement learning tasks. Additionally, the use of capsule networks suggests a potential fit for cs.CV (Computer Vision) as well. The paper also mentions the use of recurrent networks, which could place it in the sub-categories of cs.RO (Robotics) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
